Homes Under $400K in Port St. Lucie (2026 Update)

Can You Still Buy a Home in Port St. Lucie Under $400K?

Yes — but strategy matters more in this price range.

Homes under $400K in Port St. Lucie remain one of the strongest entry points for first-time buyers in South Florida. Compared to Broward or Palm Beach County, your money still stretches further here — especially in select neighborhoods and resale pockets.

