What $350K–$400K Typically Gets You in PSL

In 2026, homes under $400K in Port St. Lucie generally include:
	•	3 bedrooms
	•	2 bathrooms
	•	1,300–1,800 square feet
	•	1–2 car garage
	•	Built between the late 1990s and mid-2010s
	•	Mostly resale (limited new construction at this level)

Some may require minor cosmetic updates. Others are move-in ready but smaller in size.

This range is ideal for:
	•	First-time buyers
	•	Buyers relocating from higher-priced counties
	•	Buyers seeking manageable monthly payments
	•	Buyers prioritizing long-term equity growth

The key is understanding area differences.

