Frequently Asked Questions

Are there new construction homes under $400K in PSL?

Limited inventory exists at this level in 2026. Most options under $400K are resale properties.

Is $400K enough for a 4-bedroom home?

Occasionally, yes — depending on condition and area. 3-bedroom homes are more common in this range.

What credit score do I need?

Many loan programs accept mid-600s. FHA may allow lower depending on profile.

Are no-HOA homes available under $400K?

Yes, particularly in select Gatlin and western PSL areas.

How fast do homes under $400K sell?

Well-priced properties often move faster than higher tiers.

